enums.name: Auditing
enums.description:
Auditing option specified per service method
by default all service methods are included
add the auditing option if you want to exclude a method in auditing

values.name: AUDITING_UNSPECIFIED
values.description: AUDITING_UNSPECIFIED is not specified

values.name: AUDITING_INCLUDED
values.description: AUDITING_INCLUDED if a method is annotated with this, all calls are audited

values.name: AUDITING_EXCLUDED
values.description: AUDITING_EXCLUDED if a method is annotated with this, no calls are audited
